             was indicted for <rs id="t18060917-80-off437" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18060917-80-off437" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18060917-80-off437" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18060917-80-cd438" type="crimeDate">22nd of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060917-80-off437 t18060917-80-cd438"></join>, five shawls, value 10 s. and a half shawl, value 1 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18060917-80-victim769" type="victimName">
