                  , privately in his shop
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18060917-80-person770">
                  WILLIAM 
                  CAVE
               <interp inst="t18060917-80-person770" type="surname" value="CAVE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18060917-80-person770" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
